# Municipal Waste Collection Data Visualization Platform

## ğŸ” Project Overview

This project is a **web-based data visualization platform** developed for the **City of Granada** to monitor and explore **municipal waste collection data** at eco-point level.

The application allows citizens and municipal teams to visualize **collection frequency and collected weight** through interactive charts, tables and maps, improving transparency and data accessibility.

---

## ğŸ¯ Key Features

- Interactive web dashboard to explore waste collection data
- Map-based visualization of eco-points across the city
- QR-code access for each eco-point
- Time-based analysis of collection frequency and collected weight
- Public feedback redirection to the official â€œGranada Mejoraâ€ platform

