## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** PHP
- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Database:** MariaDB (MySQL compatible)
- **Server:** LAMP stack (Debian, Apache)
- **Data:** Municipal waste collection datasets (SIGMA DB)

